后期研究发现该属更为衍生，与[[无鼻角龙|无鼻角龙]]和[[三角龙族|三角龙族]]关系较近。然而，该属由于化石残缺而通常被从系统发育分析中删除，因为它是一个通配符分类单元（wildcard taxon），这意味着其演化位置不稳定，并研究导致结果不准确。<ref>{{cite journal | url=https://pubs.geoscienceworld.org/cjes/article-abstract/52/2/85/134795 | title=A reassessment of the horned dinosaur Judiceratops tigris (Ornithischia: Ceratopsidae) from the Upper Cretaceous (Campanian) of Montana, USA | author=Campbell, James A. | journal=Canadian Journal of Earth Sciences | year=2015 | volume=52 | issue=2 | pages=85–95 | doi=10.1139/cjes-2014-0172 | access-date=2021-02-07 | archive-date=2019-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702041454/https://pubs.geoscienceworld.org/cjes/article-abstract/52/2/85/134795 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4699738/ | title=A Re-Evaluation of the Chasmosaurine Ceratopsid Genus Chasmosaurus (Dinosauria: Ornithischia) from the Upper Cretaceous (Campanian) Dinosaur Park Formation of Western Canada | last1=Campbell | first1=James A. | last2=Ryan | first2=Michael J. | last3=Holmes | first3=Robert B. | last4=Schröder-Adams | first4=Claudia J. | journal=PLoS One | year=2016 | volume=11 | issue=1 | pages=e0145805 | doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0145805 | access-date=2021-02-07 | archive-date=2022-05-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220527191356/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4699738/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | url=https://www.nrcresearchpress.com/doi/abs/10.1139/cjes-2014-0028#.XuMwnefQ9VJ | title=New information on the rare horned dinosaur Arrhinoceratops brachyops (Ornithischia: Ceratopsidae) from the Upper Cretaceous of Alberta, Canada | last1=Mallon | first1=Jordan C. | last2=Holmes | first2=Robert | last3=Anderson | first3=Jason S. | last4=Farke | first4=Andrew A. | last5=Evans | first5=David C. | journal=Canadian Journal of Earth Sciences | year=2014 | volume=51 | issue=6 | pages=618-634 | doi=10.1139/cjes-2014-0028}}</ref>福勒和费里德曼·福勒（2020年）将其恢复到更为基础的位置，接近五角龙，并再次成为科阿韦拉角龙的姐妹群。然而，他们也决定从分析中删除它，因为其结论是该分类单元无效。<ref name="Transitional" />

